V TR VNG KT NI THUN LI
V tr d n cn h LDG SKY Thnh Ph D An, Bnh Dng
V tr a ch d n cn h Icon Plaza ngay ti vng xoay ng 6 An Ph, Thnh ph Thun An. Bnh Dng, t d n c dn d dng kt ni cc trc ng huyt mch nh: M Phc Tn Vn, Trn Quang Diu, Hai Mi Hai Thng Mi Hai, L Hng Phong, Nguyn Th Ti, DT743, DT743C, DT743B, i l Bnh Dng, Quc l 1K Vi v tr c a trong khu vc, Icon Plaza Bnh Dng ha hn s mang n tim nng tng gi v tin khong hu dnh cho c dn. Hn na, s ci cch v hnh chnh khin cho thnh ph Thun An ngy cng c u t mnh m v h tng, nng cao cht lng i sng c dn thnh ph.

Lin kt Vng & Tin ch d n cn h chung c Icon Plaza Thuan An ng Vng Xoay An Ph ch u t Danh Vit Group
D n Icon Plaza Bnh Dng tr thnh khu d n cn h cao cp c bao quanh bi thin nhin xanh mt, ngn cch vi ph th ng c, n o, kh bi. Ti y, mi ngy c dn tng lai c th i do trn nhng con ng rp bng mt, thnh thi th gin ht th bu khng kh trong lnh, xua tan nhng u t, mt mi sau nhng gi lm vic cng thng.

MT BNG TNG TH
Mt bng chi tit cn h d n Icon Plaza c thit k ly cm hng t chu u, mang phong cch hin i, tinh t v c o vi to hnh nhng cnh qut n gi gip ti u ha din tch v cng nng ti a trong tng cn h, to s thoi mi th gin sau nhng bn b lo u thng ngy v sn sng tn hng mt cuc sng tin nghi.

MT BNG THIT K CN H

Thit k chi tit d n cn h Icon Plaza a dng nhiu din tch khc nhau vi cc loi hnh Studio, cn h 1,2,3 phng ng.. Nh vy, mi cn h ca Icon Plaza Bnh Dng u chinh phc c nhng khch hng d l kh tnh nht.
Icon Plaza Thun An tr thnh ni gip c dn gt b nhng bn b lo u thng ngy v sn sng tn hng mt cuc sng tin nghi. Khng ni no bng nh mnh l thng ip m ch u t mong mun mi c dn cm nhn c khi an c ti Icon Bnh Dng. D hc tp, lm vic hay rong rui ni u, khi v n t m c dn s cm nhn c cuc sng tin nghi ngay ngng ca.

CN H MU ICON PLAZA

Nh mu d n Icon Plaza c thit k vi phong cch hin i thong mt. Bn cnh nhng im cng u vit v v tr, h thng tin ch, uy tn ch u t v n v thi cng, d n Icon Plaza Bnh Dng cn c bit thu ht khch hng quan tm nh cn h ng cp c thit k thng minh, thong rng.

Ta cn h c thit k c o, c to hnh nh nhng cnh qut n gi khng l gip cho hn 90% cn h l cn gc vi 2 mt thong. Cng ngh xy dng hin i, khng c cc tr ct b tng trong nh nh cch xy dng truyn thng cng vi thit k thng minh gip ti u ha cng nng v din tch s dng ca tng cn h ti d n Icon Plaza Bnh D. Cc phng chc nng cng c b tr mt cch khoa hc, nhm p ng ti a nhu cu sinh hot ca cc th h trong gia nh. y l l do hon ho cho qu khch hng mua Icon Plaza Bnh Dng.
